@notice Constructor for CommonWillFactory contract
 @param _master Master implementation for the Common Will

params._master: Master implementation for the Common Will

params._conditionDataId: Identifier of the condition for process success, e.g. an IPFS content identifier
params._minPledge: Minimal pledge required to reach within a predefined time. If not reached the process is considered  as failed and pledgers can withraw their pledge
params._minPledgeDueTime: predefined time for the minimal pledge to be reached
params._pledgeToken: The pledge token in the process
params._processDueTime: Final time of the process. If this time is reached with no suceess of the executor,  the process is considered as failed and pledgers can withraw their pledge
